INSERT INTO exchange_rates 
                    (id, from_currency, to_currency, rate, source, date, effective_date)
                    VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6, $6)
                    ON CONFLICT (from_currency, to_currency, date)
                    DO UPDATE SET 
                        rate = $4,
                        source = $5,
                        effective_date = $6,
                        updated_at = CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
